commit.message:
Refer to top-level URI

Needed only till amqp gem 1.1.0 goes GA.

Fixes #26.

Roll RabbitMQ extensions into the core

This will make it possible to delay extension operations in amqp gem the same
way we do with AMQP::Channel methods.

In the long run, amq-client will be deprecated and all its code
will be rolled into amqp gem itself.
Don't force nowait if the option is explicitly given
Override Consumer#to_s to provide more useful information
Moved one more test to amqp gem
This test belongs to amqp gem

When handling channel.close, don't invoke automatic connection recovery

It wasn't intentional and it resets callbacks that makes Channel#reuse
useless in amqp gem

Pause heartbeat sender when handling network connection interruption

[ci skip]
Make it possible to override rabbitmqctl location via RABBITMQCTL
Start heartbeat sender after we negotiated the interval in connection.tune handler
